section1.title: OUR MOTO
section1.description: The National Service Scheme operates with the motto 'NOT ME BUT YOU' aiming to inspire youth to serve the people and emphasises the importance of selflessness and putting the needs of others before one's own.It constantly reminder that our actions are driven by the needs of others, that our service is not for personal gain but for the greater good. Embracing this motto, we humbly dedicate ourselves to the service of humanity
